                    <p>At Ratnakamal Medical Centre of Excellence, we’ve built every corner of our facility with your safety and comfort in mind. Here’s what makes us unique:</p>

                    <p><b>Smart Design for Safer Care</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>Separate Departments:</b> Clear zoning for Pathology, Genetics, Fetal Medicine, Radiology, and Cardiac Diagnostics ensures smooth patient flow without crowding.</li>

                        <li><b>Friendly Help Desks:</b> Our team guides you through test preparation, reports, appointments, and doctor consultations—making every visit stress-free.</li>

                        <li><b>Green Practices:</b> All diagnostic units follow low-waste protocols with safe biomedical disposal, reducing environmental impact.</li>

                        <li><b>Infection Control:</b> Sterile sampling areas, sanitized ultrasound suites, and controlled testing zones ensure clean, safe, contamination-free diagnostics.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p><b>Diagnostics Done Right</b></p>

