                        <li><b>Fetal Medicine Unit:</b> Dedicated rooms for NT scans, anomaly scans, growth scans, CVS and Amniocentesis—conducted with utmost safety and accuracy.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p><b>Imaging: Where Technology Meets Expertise</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>MSK Ultrasound Suite:</b>High-resolution imaging with guided MSK interventions for joints, ligaments, tendons, and soft-tissue conditions.</li>

                        <li><b>4D & Comprehensive USG:</b> Real-time fetal views, abdominal scans, pelvic scans, and whole-body ultrasound under one roof.</li>

                        <li><b>Specialized Doctor Chamber: </b>Senior consultants available for detailed review, interpretation, and clinical decision-making.</li>

                    </ol>


                    <p><b>Cardiac & Respiratory Care</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>ECG & Echocardiography:</b> Advanced echo systems measuring heart structure, flow, and rhythm abnormalities with precision.</li>

                        <li><b>Holter Monitoring:</b> 24-hour/48-hour portable cardiac rhythm monitoring for accurate detection of intermittent issues.</li>

                        <li><b>PFT Lab:</b> Dedicated Pulmonary Function Testing room to evaluate lung health, breathing capacity, and respiratory diseases.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p><b>Patient Convenience First</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>Pre-Test Guidance:</b> Our staff ensures you are fully prepared—fasting instructions, medication advice, and test-specific preparation made easy.</li>

                        <li><b>Post-Test Support:</b> Review of reports, doctor consultations, and follow-up scheduling so your care doesn’t end after the test.</li>
                    </ol>

